.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/1-1-1024x583.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"840\" height=\"478\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-838\" /><span class=\"heading\"><span class=\"title\">Listening Zone</span><span>Click to book a demo</span></span><div class=\"hover-text\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n						<div class=\"top\"><div class=\"inside\"><span class=\"title\">Listening Zone</span><p>\r\n							Feel free to book a demo audition with us. Demo by prior appointment only and specific timing from 11am to 7:30 pm\r\n						</p>\r\n						<a href=\"[base_url]index.php/listening-zone\"><span>Read More</span></a></div></div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</li>\r\n				<li><img src=\"http://ulta.m2dev.invanos.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Untitled-1_08.jpg\" alt=\"untitled-1_08\" width=\"573\" height=\"264\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-26\" /><span class=\"heading\"><span class=\"title\">Expert Solutions</span><span>Click to view more</span></span><div class=\"hover-text\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n						<div class=\"top\"><div class=\"inside\"><span class=\"title\">Expert Solutions</span><p>\r\n							Feel free to call us for any kind of consultation.</p>\r\n						<a href=\"tel:+917410024241\" class=\"desktop-mobile\" desktop=\"912249247424\"><span>912249247424</span></a></div></div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"service-block-right\">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li><img src=\"http://ulta.m2dev.invanos.net/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/MG_4641-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"_MG_4641\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1006\" /><span class=\"heading\"><span class=\"title\">Automation Solutions</span><span>Click to view more</span></span><div class=\"hover-text\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n						<div class=\"top\"><div class=\"inside\"><span class=\"title\">Automation Solutions</span><p>\r\n							A typical home automation system is composed of a set of equipment categorized according to Lighting Control, Security, Cli